{"word":"λάχεια","slug":"λάχεια","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λάχεια</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:λαχαίνω'><el>λαχαίνω</el></a>\n<p/><a href='S:feminine'>fem.</a> <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a> <i>well-tilled, fertile</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>:—others read <el>ἐλάχεια</el>, from <a href='S:ἐλαχύς'><el>ἐλαχύς</el></a>, <i>small.</i><p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἐλαχύς'><el>ἐλαχύς</el></a>\n"}]}